            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>沙田新城市广场今日起举行「YATA 惊喜盒子玩具展」，为期两周至 11 月 26 日结束。本次展览主打盲盒收藏与各类玩具，设置了多个展示区域，让参观者可以体验各种新奇产品，并探索各类限量商品。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275236" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4848-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4848-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4848.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275237" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4849-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4849-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4849.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275238" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4850-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4850-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4850.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>会场限定商品与促销活动</h2><p>本次展览推出多款会场限定商品，如「Sanrio characters 摇篮不倒翁系列萌趣豆」、「Hangyodon 风味拉面系列微盒 Pro」等。部分热门商品如 Tamagotchi UNI 魔鬼版及 Sanrio characters 版亦于展场发售。现场部分商品享有折扣，例如购买《Sanrio characters》、食玩和《Rement》品牌的盲盒可享 85 折优惠。此外，购买《Tamagotchi》主机产品的顾客还可获得 Tama Passport 一本，而购买指定数量产品还可获赠吊饰。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275242" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4844-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4844-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4844.jpg 675